Does Pluribus software have a name? In general, the Netmiko naming convention is `vendor_platform_transport` where transport is almost always SSH (and rarely telnet).

Example, platforms for Cisco are `ios`, `nxos`, `iosrx`. Is there any similar Platform name for Pluribus?

